This paper discusses privacy concerns related to the use of personal data in various fields such as healthcare, transportation, education, law enforcement, national security, commerce, and social interactions. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), computers and society (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), computer engineering (cs.CE), and databases (cs.DB).
